 ď‘™ - MODIFIER(SUPER/WINDOWS/left hand, bottom row, far right key)

 Hyprland controls
 -----------------------------
 ď‘™ + ENTER - opens application launcher
 ď‘™ + Q - closes active window
 ď‘™ + T - opens terminal
 ď‘™ + B - opens web browser
 ď‘™ + F - opens file manager
 ď‘™ + S - opens steam
 ď‘™ + 6 - shortcuts to spotify
 ď‘™ + D - opens discord
 ď‘™ + any arrow key - moves to active window in direction pressed
 ď‘™ + any number - moves to that workspace
 ď‘™ + SHIFT + V - toggles floating window
 ď‘™ + SHIFT + F - toggles fullscreen
 ď‘™ + SHIFT + LMB(HOLD) - picks up selected window, release LMB to drop
 ď‘™ + SHIFT + RMB(HOLD) - resizes selected window, release RMB to stop
 ď‘™ + SHIFT + any number - moves active window to workspace of number pressed



